rows.label: xs03040100_MSG0001
rows.name:
They seem like a pretty warlike species.
And that "kill all" talk[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03040100_MSG0002
rows.name: True[ST:wide ]― But they did say they were ordered.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03040100_MSG0003
rows.name:
If there's a commander in there,
we might still be able to negotiate.[ST:wait ]
